						               													<description>HEXO: Card Game will improve your visual acuity and spatial perception in a dynamic, fun and easy to learn card game based on technical drawing. The game has the features to be the ideal quick game to compete with friends, family, colleagues, couple... In which you'll cannot play just one game, you'll ask for a rematch!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On HEXO: Card Game you'll be challenged to find which of the 18 shapes of your 6 unique cards matches* with the active figure card. Who will be the fastest? Matches happens when one of the shapes of the card played coincides with one of the sides of the active figure. When no shapes matches, the move is wrong and a penalty will be applied.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If it's a match, you score one point! Place the card played by the dark side back on your zone and a new round begins.&amp;#10;In the following rounds you won't be able to score extra points with dark cards, but you can still play them to prevent other players from gaining points!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player who turns over 4 of his shape cards will be the winner of HEXO: Card Game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Are you ready for a rematch?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
